  "description": "A funnel (also conversion funnel or marketing funnel) is a model of the reader\u0026rsquo;s journey from first contact with a message to the desired action — awareness → interest → consideration → conversion. The metaphor is spatial: many people enter the top (they see the headline, the ad, the post) and progressively fewer proceed to each subsequent stage, until a fraction convert at the bottom.\nThe funnel model matters for copywriters because each stage requires different copy:\n",
